high_descs: Turn then move to the counter where the microwave is
Pick up the knife that is on top of the counter by the microwave
Carry the knife to the counter to the left of the fridge where the two potatoes are
Slice the potato on the far left
Move to the kitchen sink
Place the knife in the sink
Move back to the counter top where the sliced potato is on top of the counter
Pick up a potato slice
Carry the potato slice to the microwave
Place the potato in the microwave then shut the door to cook then remove the potato
Carry the potato to the kitchen sink
Place the potato in the sink basin
anns.task_desc: slice a potato to heat the slice, place potato in sink

high_descs: Turn around, go straight to the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn around, go straight to the counter, turn left, go straight to the counter.
Cut the potato on the left into slices.
Go left and face towards the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Go back right to where the potato was.
Take a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn around, walk towards the door, turn right to the microwave at the end of the counter.
Cook the potato in the microwave, Take the potato from the microwave.
Turn around, go straight, when at the table turn left, go ahead to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in a sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter where the microwave is.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn around and go to the fridge, then hang a left and go to the counter.
Use the knife to cut the leftmost potato into slices.
Turn to the left and go to the sink that will be on the right.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn to the right and go to the counter with the potato that you cut.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Turn around and go to the dining table, then go right to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave, turn it on to cook, remove the potato when it is done cooking.
Turn around and go to the table, then hang a left and go to the sink.
Put the cooked potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in a sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the counter.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Turn around and cross the room to face the counter to the left of the fridge.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Move to the left and turn to face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Go to the right and face the sink to the right of the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Move to stand in front of the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and turn it on and then take the potato out again.
Turn to the right and stand in front of the sink.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the kitchen counter that the microwave is on.
Pick up the knife on the counter, in front of the sponge.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator, turn left at the refrigerator and walk to the kitchen counter just above the dishwasher.
Cut the potato that is on the counter, between the tomato and the other potato, into slices.
Walk to the sink, to your left.
Place the knife in the sink, in front of the spatula.
Turn to your right and go back to the counter, above the dishwasher.
Pick up a potato slice from the middle of the potato.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, make a right at the kitchen table and go to the microwave.
Place the potato slice in the microwave, warm it up, then remove it from the microwave.
Turn to your right and go back to the sink.
Place the potato in the sink, to the left of the spatula, and behind the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm potato slice in the sink.
